# AI

- One agent per file in packages/prompts.
- Each agent: own prompt, own context, own model config.
- Model IDs read from AiModelConfig DB table — never hardcode in worker logic.
- OpenRouter client in packages/shared — fallback to DEFAULT_MODELS.
- Workers extract JSON from AI responses with validation.
- Never block API requests with AI calls — always queue.
